headline: The 'Sell America' Trade Is Real, Cohn Says
summary: IBM Vice Chairman Gary Cohn says he is still optimistic about the US economy despite geopolitical tensions, citing high GDP growth as a major tailwind. But he does say the "Sell America" trade is real. He speaks on "Bloomberg Surveillance" at the 2026 World Economic Forum in Davos, Switzerland.
